headline: Commvault Systems (CVLT) Q2 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Commvault (CVLT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -3.19% and +0.99%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
